  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate", 
    "date": "2015-09-10T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "This bill increases the special monthly pension for living Medal of Honor recipients.\n\nThe Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) shall not make an annual pension increase for such recipients, effective December 1, 2016, if the increased monthly pension under this Act takes effect before such date. If the VA does not make the December 1, 2016 increase, however, annual increases shall resume as of December 1, 2017."
